data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the coveted Southdown Trace neighborhood! This stunning 4-bedroom gem boasts a refreshing pool, perfect for those sunny Texas days. Step inside to a formal dining room, large Family Room and the Kitchen, which is a chef's delight w/designer cabinets, granite countertops and plenty of storage. Upstairs discover a spacious Game room with balcony, ideal for entertaining friends and family. Enjoy the seamless flow of vinyl plank floors downstairs, creating a modern and inviting atmosphere. Crown molding adds a touch of elegance to the home's aesthetic. Home is energy-efficient including a radiant barrier roofing deck and a 16 SEER HVAC system(AC installed 9/23). The covered patio invites you to unwind and savor the outdoors. Conveniently located near San Jacinto College, Hobby Airport, shopping centers, entertainment hubs, and a variety of restaurants, this residence offers both luxury and accessibility. Don't miss the chance to make this your forever home!
